      • messageExists

        public org.springframework.test.web.servlet.ResultMatcher messageExists(String... messages)
        ResultMessages has specific messages with default locale.

        Correspond to ResultMessage.fromCode(String, Object...) and ResultMessage.fromText(String). Message is resolved from ResultMessage.getCode() and ResultMessage.getArgs() using MessageSource.

        Parameters:
        messages - resolved messages of result message
        Returns:
        result matcher
        See Also:
        MessageSource

      • messageExists

        public org.springframework.test.web.servlet.ResultMatcher messageExists(Locale locale,
                                                                        String... messages)
        ResultMessages has specific messages with specific locale.

        Correspond to ResultMessage.fromCode(String, Object...) and ResultMessage.fromText(String). Message is resolved from ResultMessage.getCode() and ResultMessage.getArgs() using MessageSource with specific locale.

        Parameters:
        locale - locale using resolve message
        messages - resolved messages of result message
        Returns:
        result matcher
